                                                                                                <div class="col-lg-12">
                                                                                                    <div class="faq__main__blk">
                                                                                                        <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">

                                                                                                            <div class="accordion-item">
                                                                                                                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                                                                                                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                                                                                                        <span class="faq__plus faq__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></span>
                                                                                                                        <span class="faq__minus faq__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus"></i></span>
                                                                                                                        Do I need to register to recharge my mobile?
                                                                                                                    </button>
                                                                                                                </h2>
                                                                                                                <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                                                                                                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                                                                                                        No! You can do a Top Up recharge as a guest without registering. Simply click on Online Recharge, enter your 10-digit mobile number, select a plan, and pay. However, for services like Post Bill Payment, Caller Tunes, and Do Not Disturb, you need to register and login.
                                                                                                                    </div>
                                                                                                                </div>
                                                                                                            </div>

                                                                                                            <div class="accordion-item active">
                                                                                                                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                                                                                                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
