                                                                                                                        <span class="faq__minus faq__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus"></i></span>
                                                                                                                        How do I create My Account?
                                                                                                                    </button>
                                                                                                                </h2>
                                                                                                                <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                                                                                                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                                                                                                        Click on Register in the navigation bar. Enter your 10-digit mobile number (this will be your username), your email address, and a password. Once registered, you can login and access all services including Post Bill Payment, Caller Tunes, Do Not Disturb and more.
                                                                                                                    </div>
                                                                                                                </div>
                                                                                                            </div>

                                                                                                            <div class="accordion-item">
